body:
### Welcome to use Secret Notebook
Secret Notebook is an application to record your personal information safely. You can write notes and attach photos with them. All the data is stored with encryption. You can create more than one secret account to save different kind of information. You can switch account freely and this makes your personal information very secret.

If you have any question or advice, please send E-mail to mint@vip.qq.com
